creator: Arthur J. Burks; Murray Leinster; Harl Vincent; Victor Rousseau; Edmond Hamilton; R. F. Starzl; Harold Thompson Rich
description:
LibriVox recording of Astounding Stories 08, August 1930 by Arthur J. Burks; Murray Leinster; Harl Vincent; Victor Rousseau; Edmond Hamilton; R. F. Starzl; Harold Thompson Rich.
Read in English by Bill Boerst; Douglas Taylor; Zachary Brewster-Geisz; Larry Greene; Will Staunton; Atmor; Tommy Howell; Scott Foster; Marty
Issue eight of this seminal science-fiction magazine Issue eight of this seminal science-fiction magazine CONTENTS Murder Madness by Murray Leinster - the conclusion of this novel Earth the Maurader by Arthur J. Burks - Part 2 of a 3 Part novel as well as short Stories The Planet of Dread by R.F. Starxl, The Lord of Space by Victor Rousseau, The Seconf Satellite by Edmund Hamilton, Silver Dome by Harl Vincent and The Flying City by H. Thompson Rich (summary by Annise)
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
